@startuml Gesture_Management_Activity_States
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
}

[*] --> Initializing : onCreate()

Initializing --> Ready : Setup Complete

Ready --> Drawing : User Starts Drawing Gesture
Drawing --> GestureDrawn : Drawing Complete

GestureDrawn --> Saving : Save Button Clicked
GestureDrawn --> Clearing : Clear Button Clicked

Saving --> EnteringName : Show Save Dialog
EnteringName --> BindingFunction : Name Entered
BindingFunction --> FunctionBound : Function Selected
FunctionBound --> GestureSaved : Save to Database
GestureSaved --> Ready : Gesture Saved

Clearing --> Ready : Gesture Cleared

Ready --> ViewingGestures : View Saved Gestures
ViewingGestures --> EditingGesture : Edit Gesture Selected
ViewingGestures --> DeletingGesture : Delete Gesture Selected
ViewingGestures --> Ready : Return

EditingGesture --> UpdatingGesture : Update Gesture
UpdatingGesture --> GestureUpdated : Update Complete
GestureUpdated --> Ready : Return

DeletingGesture --> GestureDeleted : Delete Confirmed
GestureDeleted --> Ready : Return

Ready --> TogglingLogin : Gesture Login Switch Toggled
TogglingLogin --> LoginEnabled : Switch On
TogglingLogin --> LoginDisabled : Switch Off
LoginEnabled --> Ready : Setting Saved
LoginDisabled --> Ready : Setting Saved

Ready --> Paused : onPause()
Paused --> Ready : onResume()

Ready --> [*] : onDestroy()

@enduml
